==Arabic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''{{ARchar|ﺏ / ﺑ / ﺒ / ﺐ}}''' (bā’)

# The second letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. Its name is {{ARchar|[[باء]]}} (bā’) and it has the sound of English '''[[B]]'''. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[أ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ت]]}}.
# The second letter of the Kurdo-Arabic alphabet. Its name is {{ARchar|[[با]]}} (bā) and it has the sound of English '''[[B]]'''. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ا]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[پ]]}}. Equivalent to [[b]] in the Kurdo-Latin alphabet.

